{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban fossil fuel advertising and sponsorship",
        "additional_details": "Fossil fuel advertising has a history of \u2018greenwashing\u2019 and a recent report identifies \u00a34bn+ spent by FF companies on 205 active sports sponsorship deals. There is plenty of evidence that FF must be rapidly phased out to mitigate the worst impacts of climate breakdown. I think that preventing the companies\u2019 efforts to enhance their social capital and normalise their activities would proactively help address the climate crisis and mitigate future harm to human health.",
        "background": "Advertisements encourage the use of products and sponsorship promotes a positive reputation & creates a social licence of trust & acceptability. In 2003 a ban on all tobacco advertising was introduced and has arguably worked. I believe continued fossil fuel usage will kill more people than smoking.",
